THIRD-PARTY LICENSES AND LICENSE COMPATIBILITY NOTES:

This matrix contains mappings to and rationale about the following
third-party frameworks. The following notes apply:

OWASP AISVS v1.0 (CC BY-SA 4.0):
  Requirement text is NOT reproduced in this corpus. Mappings reference
  AISVS by requirement_id (e.g., C1.1) and independently authored rationale
  only. No CC BY-SA 4.0 content is incorporated as a derivative work.

OWASP LLM Top 10 2025 (CC BY-SA 4.0):
  Referenced by entry identifier (e.g., LLM03:2025) and independently
  authored rationale only. No requirement text reproduced.

CSA AI Controls Matrix v1.0.3 (CC BY-SA 4.0):
  Referenced by control identifier (e.g., MG-01) and independently authored
  rationale only. No requirement text reproduced.

MITRE ATLAS v5.6.0 (Apache 2.0):
  Technique identifiers (AML.T####) and technique names are referenced.
  Apache 2.0 is compatible with CC BY-NC 4.0 for reference use.

NIST AI RMF, EU AI Act, SR 26-2 (public domain / government publications):
  Referenced by identifier and independently authored rationale.
  No verbatim reproduction of requirement text.

ISO/IEC 42001:2023 (proprietary, paid):
  Referenced by clause identifier only. No requirement text is reproduced.
  Implementers must obtain the standard from ISO directly.
